  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "bayes",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bayes/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.37,
      "size": 37872,
      "text": "欢迎来到贝叶斯定理实验！今天我们要学习一种强大的推理方法。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bayes",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bayes/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.46,
      "size": 39312,
      "text": "想象你是一名医生，病人的检测结果呈阳性，他真的患病的概率是多少？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bayes",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bayes/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36720,
      "text": "答案可能会让你惊讶。贝叶斯定理帮助我们正确地思考这类问题。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bayes",
      "section_id": "conditional-prob",
      "line_id": "conditional-prob-1",
      "filename": "conditional-prob-conditional-prob-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bayes/conditional-prob-conditional-prob-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.07,
      "size": 17136,
      "text": "首先我们要理解条件概率。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bayes",
      "section_id": "conditional-prob",
      "line_id": "conditional-prob-2",
      "filename": "conditional-prob-conditional-prob-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bayes/conditional-prob-conditional-prob-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "P(A|B)表示在B发生的条件下，A发生的概率。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bayes",
      "section_id": "conditional-prob",
      "line_id": "conditional-prob-3",
      "filename": "conditional-prob-conditional-prob-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bayes/conditional-prob-conditional-prob-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.4,
      "size": 38448,
      "text": "例如，P(患病|阳性)表示检测阳性的人中，真正患病的比例。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bayes",
      "section_id": "conditional-prob",
      "line_id": "conditional-prob-4",
      "filename": "conditional-prob-conditional-prob-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bayes/conditional-prob-conditional-prob-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.03,
      "size": 32544,
      "text": "注意，P(A|B)和P(B|A)通常是不同的！"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bayes",
      "section_id": "bayes-formula",
      "line_id": "bayes-formula-1",
      "filename": "bayes-formula-bayes-formula-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bayes/bayes-formula-bayes-formula-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.53,
      "size": 24480,
      "text": "贝叶斯定理给出了条件概率的计算公式。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bayes",
      "section_id": "bayes-formula",
      "line_id": "bayes-formula-2",
      "filename": "bayes-formula-bayes-formula-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bayes/bayes-formula-bayes-formula-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.17,
      "size": 34704,
      "text": "P(A|B)等于P(B|A)乘以P(A)除以P(B)。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bayes",
      "section_id": "bayes-formula",
      "line_id": "bayes-formula-3",
      "filename": "bayes-formula-bayes-formula-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bayes/bayes-formula-bayes-formula-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.2,
      "size": 35136,
      "text": "P(A)叫做先验概率，是我们在看到证据之前对A的信念。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bayes",
      "section_id": "bayes-formula",
      "line_id": "bayes-formula-4",
      "filename": "bayes-formula-bayes-formula-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bayes/bayes-formula-bayes-formula-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.25,
      "size": 36000,
      "text": "P(A|B)叫做后验概率，是看到证据B之后更新的信念。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bayes",
      "section_id": "medical-test",
      "line_id": "medical-test-1",
      "filename": "medical-test-medical-test-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bayes/medical-test-medical-test-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.74,
      "size": 27792,
      "text": "让我们用一个医学检测的例子来理解贝叶斯定理。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bayes",
      "section_id": "medical-test",
      "line_id": "medical-test-2",
      "filename": "medical-test-medical-test-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bayes/medical-test-medical-test-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.51,
      "size": 40176,
      "text": "假设某种疾病的患病率是1%，检测的准确率是99%。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bayes",
      "section_id": "medical-test",
      "line_id": "medical-test-3",
      "filename": "medical-test-medical-test-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bayes/medical-test-medical-test-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.65,
      "size": 26352,
      "text": "如果你检测呈阳性，你真正患病的概率是多少？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bayes",
      "section_id": "medical-test",
      "line_id": "medical-test-4",
      "filename": "medical-test-medical-test-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bayes/medical-test-medical-test-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.22,
      "size": 35568,
      "text": "很多人会说99%，但正确答案大约只有50%！"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bayes",
      "section_id": "calculation",
      "line_id": "calculation-1",
      "filename": "calculation-calculation-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bayes/calculation-calculation-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.07,
      "size": 17136,
      "text": "让我们用贝叶斯定理来计算。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bayes",
      "section_id": "calculation",
      "line_id": "calculation-2",
      "filename": "calculation-calculation-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bayes/calculation-calculation-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.77,
      "size": 28368,
      "text": "在1000人中，大约10人患病，990人健康。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bayes",
      "section_id": "calculation",
      "line_id": "calculation-3",
      "filename": "calculation-calculation-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bayes/calculation-calculation-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.79,
      "size": 44640,
      "text": "10个患病者中，约10人检测阳性。990个健康者中，约10人假阳性。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bayes",
      "section_id": "calculation",
      "line_id": "calculation-4",
      "filename": "calculation-calculation-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bayes/calculation-calculation-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.19,
      "size": 34992,
      "text": "所以20个阳性中只有10个真正患病，概率是50%。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bayes",
      "section_id": "base-rate",
      "line_id": "base-rate-1",
      "filename": "base-rate-base-rate-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bayes/base-rate-base-rate-1.mp3",
